lead_paragraph: A fisherman discovered the 18-month-old girl hanging upside down in her car seat above the water that flowed through the car in Spanish Fork, Utah.
snippet: A fisherman discovered the 18-month-old girl hanging upside down in her car seat above the water that flowed through the car in Spanish Fork, Utah....
abstract: Utah officials say Lily Groesbeck, 18-month-old child, is in critical but stable condition after being found by fisherman 14 hours after surviving car crash in river; child's mother Lynn Jennifer Groesbeck was found dead in car.

headline.main: After Car Crash Kills Mother, Toddler Is Found Alive in Utah River
headline.print_headline: Baby Found Alive Hours After Crash
